<div class="index-page">
  <h1 class="index-h2">Welcome to the Game World of Ironhack Students</h1>
  <h4 class="index-text">Feel free to explore your fellow Ironhack students' projects. Enjoy!</h4>
  <p class="index-text">Wanna see your game here too?
  <p>Create your account <a href="/signup">here</a> and share your game with the Ironhack Students' Community</p>

  {{!-- CAROUSEL --}}
  <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide carousel-height" data-ride="carousel">
